/target
**/*.rs.bk
.DS_Store
.envrc

# Claude Code: ignore everything under .claude/ by default. Claude
# Code is an evolving product that can drop new per-user / runtime
# files (session locks, scheduled-task state, agent worktrees) at
# any time without warning, so a whitelist is safer than chasing
# new files as they appear. Re-add explicit exceptions below as the
# team decides which configs should be shared.
.claude/*
!.claude/settings.json
!.claude/agents/
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/commands/
